<h2>About: Review</h2>

<p>To mark a citation as reviewed, click on the "review" button next to the citation.
  The grey "reviewed" button indicates that the citation is reviewed. 
</p>

<span class="button_review">review</span>
<span class="button_reviewed">reviewed</span>
<p>All citations must be marked as reviewed before your record certification can be updated.</p>
<p>Marking a citation as <strong>reviewed</strong> indicates that the citation is accurate (as of the current date) and belongs in your record.  Works that are pending publication may be marked as reviewed and updated later when the publishing status changes.</p> 
